---
const benefits = [
  'No setup fees',
  'Onboarding in 2 weeks',
  'Dedicated success manager',
  'Indonesian curriculum support',
];
---

<section class="bg-primary py-20 md:py-28 relative overflow-hidden" id="cta">
  <!-- Decorative rings -->
  <div class="absolute -top-32 -right-32 w-96 h-96 rounded-full border border-white/5 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 w-72 h-72 rounded-full border border-accent/10 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-150 h-150 rounded-full border border-white/3 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 text-center">

    <div data-reveal>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-sans font-semibold text-xs text-accent bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-6">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent animate-pulse inline-block"></span>
        Now Accepting New Schools
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-5 leading-tight">
        Ready to Transform <br class="hidden sm:block"/>How Your School Operates?
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-white/60 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Join 500+ Indonesian schools that have already made the switch. Book a free 30-minute demo and see Deltra in action with your real use cases.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 mb-10" data-reveal>
      {benefits.map(b => (
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-sans text-sm text-white/70">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
            <path d="M3 8l4 4 6-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          {b}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center" data-reveal>
      <a href="#contact" class="font-sans font-bold text-sm text-primary bg-accent px-8 py-4 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#18b899] hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-accent/30">
        Book a Free Demo
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#features" class="font-sans font-bold text-sm text-white bg-white/10 border border-white/20 px-8 py-4 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-white/20 hover:-translate-y-1">
        Explore Features
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl px-7 py-6 max-w-lg mx-auto" data-reveal>
      <div class="flex gap-1 justify-center mb-3">
        {Array.from({ length: 5 }).map(() => (
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
          </svg>
        ))}
      </div>
      <p class="font-sans text-white/70 text-sm italic leading-relaxed">
        "We saw a 60% reduction in admin workload within the first month. Our teachers finally have time to teach."
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans font-semibold text-xs text-white/40 mt-3">— Kepala Sekolah, SMA Cendekia Jakarta</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
